The Council of Mithril Dreams <br> <br>
Teapray Oogrog <br>
An Elven Cleric in the Service of Turnare for 29 seasons <br>

Wife to Lenny the Traveling Ogre <br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ulunathreee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lunathreee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>mistayn the mindless</span><br>  Posts: 292<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/27/02 2:00:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2395.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: *smiles*</span><hr size=1> that is exactly my problem.<br>
<br>
although i do appreciate the beauty of some of the two-word names, i just think they're mostly silly and it gives you a three mile long nametag above your head.<br>
<br>
and yes, i did recommend that Form use one.  but that is really the quick and dirty way out.<br>
